Titolo: Critical Blow

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Critical Blow is a 1997 Japanese video game for the Sony PlayStation developed by Racdym and published by Banpresto. It is a three dimensional fighting game, and is a sequel to Genei Tougi: Shadow Struggle. It features character designs by manga artist Ry≈çji Minagawa. The game was never released outside of Japan.